{"_path":"/city/t027","_dir":"city","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"反詐騙","description":null,"image":"/images/city/t027-1.jpeg","sequence":27,"category":"反詐騙","author":"警政署","link":null,"head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-05-31T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"反詐騙"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"反詐騙"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"最新詐騙手法"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"最新詐騙手法"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://udn.com/news/story/7320/7993835"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"交通紅單「紙本罰單」有詐騙"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"防詐騙十招"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"防詐騙十招"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"「天下沒有白吃的午餐」"}]},{"type":"text","value":"： 戒除貪念，遠離中獎詐騙"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不接「不顯示來電」電話"}]},{"type":"text","value":"： 幫助你拒絕詐騙"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"「法院電話語音通知出庭」是詐騙"}]},{"type":"text","value":"： 勿聽信電話內歹徒指示，辦理任何金融開戶或轉帳"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"多管閒事當雞婆"}]},{"type":"text","value":"： 住宅電信箱勤觀察，提防詐騙歹徒盜、轉接電話"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"小心申辦信用卡或行動電話"}]},{"type":"text","value":"： 親自前往指定門市申辦最保險，勿至不明商家，以免個資外洩"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"小心網路聊天室陷阱"}]},{"type":"text","value":"： 切勿留下家中地址、電話或個人影像，以免成為勒索肥羊"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"小心網路援交陷阱"}]},{"type":"text","value":"： ＡＴＭ無法辨識軍警身分，切勿聽歹徒指示操作，以免遭恐嚇詐財"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"網路購物要小心"}]},{"type":"text","value":"： 線上刷卡先確認網站真假；「一手交錢，一手驗貨」交易有保障"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"防詐騙三要領"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：「冷靜」、「查證」、「報警」"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"請牢記警政署防詐騙專線「165」"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：「165」全年不打烊，受理諮詢、檢舉或報案"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"預防詐騙方法"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"預防詐騙方法"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"一、預防自動櫃員機轉帳詐財"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n(ㄧ)"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不要聽信「電話」通知退稅領錢、中獎或資料外洩，而依照別人指示操作 ATM 提款機轉帳或更改資料"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，否則錢財將不翼而飛。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n(二)在電話中"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不要向別人告知您的銀行帳號、身份證號碼等個人資料"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，否則您就可能成為「人頭戶」。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n(三)不要依據所留電話查證，應先向一０四或一０五查詢電話中所提單位之正確電話號碼查證。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n二、預防手機簡訊勒索"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n(一)提醒民眾若遇此情況，應冷靜以對，可撥警政署「全國反詐騙諮詢專線 0800-018-110」或一一０電話報案及查詢，以免受騙。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n(二)獲知手機簡訊詐財情事，民眾可電各電信公司風險管理中心或向各警察機關檢舉，請求「斷話」、「斷訊」，以防被害擴大。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n(三)家中信箱之廣告信函應妥慎處理，切勿隨意棄置，以免成為有心歹徒作案工具，此外應盡可能保護個人資料，切勿外洩，避免遭到無謂困擾。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n三、預防網路詐財"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n(一)注意網路商品與一般市價是否相當，若差距過大則風險較多。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n(二)選擇有信譽之拍賣網站或購物網站，並瞭解欲交易之貨主之信用、風評等，並注意網址是否仿冒網站。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n(三)絕對不要在未確認物品的情形前就將款項匯出，儘可能以當面交易並銀貨兩訖的方式交易。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"縱使詐騙手法千變萬化，但是只要遇事遵行「停」、「聽」、「看」守則；勿急、勿躁、多思考、詳查證，一定可以避免被騙及財物損失；而面對千變萬化的新興詐騙犯罪，除由政府統籌金融機構、檢警調單位、稅務機關、電信業者等單位，密切合作加強打擊犯罪，讓歹徒無所遁形外，更有賴民眾提高警覺意識，相互提醒，方能克盡其功，希望大家一起來合力打擊詐騙犯罪，以遏制詐騙歪風。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"t027-1.jpeg","src":"/images/city/t027-1.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"反詐騙","depth":2,"text":"反詐騙","children":[{"id":"最新詐騙手法","depth":3,"text":"最新詐騙手法"},{"id":"防詐騙十招","depth":3,"text":"防詐騙十招"},{"id":"預防詐騙方法","depth":3,"text":"預防詐騙方法"}]}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:city:t027.md","_source":"content","_file":"city/t027.md","_extension":"md"}